# baselines/ - generated by `npm run replay:fixtures` (iteration 5)
#
# This directory holds:
#   baseline-latest.json   ← machine-readable, consumed by /api/baseline
#   baseline-N{count}.md   ← human-readable Markdown report
#
# Both files are REGENERATED on every `npm run replay:fixtures` run, so
# if escalation files are deleted, the next run shrinks the baseline to
# reflect only what remains on disk. Honest accounting — no stale numbers.
